&lt;h3 id=&#34;pi-hole&#34;&gt;Pi-hole&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I have Pi-hole installed on more than one device. The reason for this is that with more than one device, I can a more robust setup. For example, I have it installed on my raspberry pi and my Proxmox VE, so that if one device goes down, the other can still block ads.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
