    <item>
      <title>Pi-hole</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/pi-hole/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 17:52:28 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/pi-hole/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I have Pi-hole installed on more than one device. The reason for this is that with more than one device, I can a more robust setup. For example, I have it installed on my raspberry pi and my Proxmox VE, so that if one device goes down, the other can still block ads.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Right now Pi-hole is running on my Proxmox VE in two different nodes and a Raspberry Pi Model 2B.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
